      "content": "i hear u on the empathy part, but i'm also hearing from other parents who are really worried. they feel like these topics are too complex for kids or that they should be handled at home instead of in school. why do you think there's so much pushback from them? is it just because they don't get it, or is there a valid point being made there?",
